00:00:07.859 --> 00:00:12.359
This is a pretty easy project that you can do with some basic supplies in a single afternoon. All the supplies

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:16.379
we'll need is a number 10 can, some normal balloons either some small mirrors

00:00:16.380 --> 00:00:21.160
or a single mirror that you can cut into smaller pieces, some double-sided tape and a laser pointer.

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:23.580
Now we have all of our supplies, let's start building.

00:00:23.580 --> 00:00:29.160
First, we need our number 10 can with the top and bottom removed, so we just have a metal cylinder this particular can is full of rice

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:32.340
So I'm gonna cut off the lid, pour off the rice into a container to save it for later

00:00:32.340 --> 00:00:33.960
and then cut off the bottom.

00:00:34.980 --> 00:00:39.120
March 21st 1996. I don't know if that's when its packaged or it's theoretically expired.

